<body class="flex-col flex-1 w-full min-h-screen flex">
  <script id="content_script">
  window.___content = {"popup":{"id":"4bc8f461-7611-4689-936b-b103cce24084","image":"popup/image/dekstop whistle blowing okt 2024 rev-02.png","title":"Whistle Blowing PELINDO","lang":"id","status":"published"},"banners":[{"id":"acc18679-5817-479c-9d19-f8d437ec5842","description":"Terminal yang Handal dengan Layanan Prima.","video":"home/home-video.mp4","order":"1","subtitle":"SURABAYA","image_desktop":"home_banner/image_desktop/bg-header.jpg","image_mobile":"home_banner/image_mobile/bg-header.jpg","title":"TERMINAL PETIKEMAS","label_button":"What's New","url":"/profil/visi","lang":"id","status":"published"}],"profile":{"id":"3f238232-1bd6-42dc-815f-34c81b017c78","banner":"profile/tentangkami/main-banner-profil.jpg","video_cover":"profile/tentangkami/ephic7hhs1cxg5y4yycw.png","summary":"Terminal pertama di Indonesia yang menerapkan standar keamanan kapal dan fasilitas pelabuhan (ISPS Code) yang mulai diterapkan sejak bulan Juli 2004.","sub_heading":"Terminal Yang Handal Dengan Layanan Prima","title":"Terminal Petikemas Surabaya","heading":"Terminal Operator","tagline":"World Class Performance Terminal Operator","video_url":"zEucbuhqMzU","content":"<p>PT Terminal Petikemas Surabaya (TPS) memegang andil besar sebagai pengelola terminal petikemas. TPS adalah penyedia layanan jasa dalam mata rantai logistik, khususnya petikemas ekspor/impor di Indonesia.</p>       <p>Sebagai salah satu anak usaha PT Pelindo Terminal Petikemas (SPTP) yang merupakan Subholding dalam PT Pelabuhan Indonesia (Pelindo) Grup, TPS merupakan terminal pertama di Indonesia yang menerapkan standar keamanan kapal dan fasilitas pelabuhan (ISPS Code) yang mulai diterapkan sejak bulan Juli 2004.</p>","quote":"Reliable Terminal With Service Excellence","items":[{"icon":"tentang_kami/items/icon/pdf-7.svg","title":"Profile","url":"https://heyzine.com/flip-book/e69a3b5f40.html"},{"icon":"tentang_kami/items/icon/pdf-svgrepo-com (1)-9.svg","title":"Executive Summary","url":"https://heyzine.com/flip-book/3c88568739.html"}],"lang":"id","status":"published"},"service":[{"id":"5cba1401-2b10-4d90-a651-45f50d4e8649","description":"Rasakan kemudahan untuk melakukan pendaftaran Kartu ID Pengemudi Truk secara online. Anda dapat melakukannya kapan saja dan dimana saja. Klik di sini untuk melakukan pendaftaran secara online.","title":"Registrasi ID Card","icon":"service/icon/registrasi.svg","url":"https://gss.tps.co.id:9090/","order":"4","lang":"id","status":"published"},{"id":"d8a29055-809a-4ed3-ba5d-26cecbd38763","description":"Nikmati kemudahan mengakses layanan terpadu untuk informasi vendor, seperti informasi pendaftaran dan pengadaan serta informasi penting lainnya hanya dengan eProcurement di TPS.","title":"eProcurement","icon":"service/icon/eprocurement-1.svg","url":"https://eproc.pelindo.co.id/","order":"3","lang":"id","status":"published"},{"id":"7188ce4b-82ee-42f3-b287-24c81b8d6f96","description":"Enjoy the convenience of accessing one-stop-service for customer information, such as registration, tariffs, documents, vessels schedules, containers tracking, and other important info only with Web Access in TPS","title":"Web Access","icon":"service/icon/webaccess.svg","url":"https://www.tps.co.id:8081/webaccess","order":"2","lang":"id","status":"published"},{"id":"a549f480-ae91-40c3-8e5b-98658038f53a","description":"Rasakan kemudahan untuk melakukan pemesanan Anda melalui layanan online baru kami CLIQUE247 Anda bisa melakukannya dimana saja dan kapan saja.","title":"Online Booking","icon":"service/icon/onlinebooking-1.svg","url":"http://clique247.tps.co.id/","order":"1","lang":"id","status":"published"}],"throughput":[{"icon":"/annualthroughput/o2shi0q7bvuhc3velymk.svg","title":"TEUs/2024","value":"1.310.235","url":"/throughput"},{"icon":"/annualthroughput/b8hr9ba1xgtnbkpy9uip.svg","title":"International TEUs/2024","value":"1.245.498","url":"/throughput"},{"icon":"/annualthroughput/eeuar4iusy84ubstk6a7.svg","title":"Domestic TEUs/2024","value":"64.737","url":"/throughput"}],